"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:1.1.8.2\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">1.1.8.2</span> 标题：打谷机、脱粒板（threshing board, sledge）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">经文出处</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：חָרוּץ</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：charuts)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job41:22\">JOB 41:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa28:27\">ISA 28:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:15\">ISA 41:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos1:3\">AMO 1:3</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：מוֹרַג</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：morag)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam24:22\">2SA 24:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr21:23\">1CH 21:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:15\">ISA 41:15</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：עֲגָלָה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：‘agalah, ‘eglah)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa28:27\">ISA 28:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa28:28\">ISA 28:28</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0323_threshing_board_bottom.jpg\" alt=\"脱粒板底部\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">脱粒板底部 (© Renyrt, CC BY-SA 3.0, via Wikimedia Commons)</figcaption></figure>脱粒板是一个木制的平板型农具，用一块木板或者几块木板并排连接而成，大小约为1.5×1米（5×3英尺）。在板的一面凿出一些小孔，里面牢牢嵌入坚硬的尖石子（燧石或玄武岩）或金属片。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">用途</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0325_threshing_board.jpg\" alt=\"铁制脱粒板\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">铁制脱粒板 (© CarlosVdeHabsburgo, CC BY-SA 4.0, via Wikimedia Commons)</figcaption></figure>将脱粒板带有尖石的一侧朝下，用绳子套在牲畜上，然后碾过割下来的麦子。为了增加器具的重量（和效率），农夫可以站在或坐在板上面。当嵌着石头的脱粒板碾过麦子时，麦秆与麦粒分离，麦粒与外皮分离，同时麦秆被轧碎成糠。参上面的<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">1.1.8 脱粒和扬场 (threshing and winnowing)&lt;REALIA:1.1.8&gt;</a> 。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻译</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/OAI-0073_man_holding_winnowing_fork.png\" alt=\"OAI-0073_man_holding_winnowing_fork\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\"> (Image generated by ChatGPT using OpenAI technology)</figcaption></figure>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa28:27\">ISA 28:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa28:28\">ISA 28:28</a> 使用了多个词语来表示功能类似的器具。希伯来文<em>‘agalah</em> ／<em>‘eglah</em> 可能是一个装着锋利圆盘的打谷机，顶部有一个座位。第27节提到这种农具是为了说明：经文提到的孜然和莳萝种子太小了，不能像小麦和大麦等较大的谷物那样用脱粒板来脱粒。希伯来文<em>charuts</em> 可能是指装着铁钉而非石子的脱粒板。第27节的<em>’ofan</em> 指的是小推车的轮子（参<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">8.3 轮、车轮 (wheel)&lt;REALIA:8.3&gt;</a> ）。</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos1:3\">AMO 1:3</a> 提到“铁的脱粒板”（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> 直译），这不是说脱粒板的平板是用铁制成的，而是说木制平板上突出来的不是常用的石头，而是大铁钉。<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos1:3\">AMO 1:3</a> 中的这个表达可能是比喻，如果这个比喻在某种文化中会失去意义，那么经文的后半部分可以扩展译为，“因为他们毁灭了基列人，就像有人用装着铁钉的脱粒板打谷一样。”或者也可以不使用比喻，译成“他们野蛮、残忍地对待基列人”（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 直译）。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
